.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Birthday: december, november, july, june, april
House: cottage, farmhouse, tower, gothic-revival, ranch-style
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: decembermaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. House:cottage == Birthday:july
2. House:swedish == Pet:dog
3. House:farmhouse == Beverage:tea
4. Birthday:november is on the left of Birthday:june
5. Birthday:november == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Birthday:april == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. House:gothic-revival is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:decembermaster == Beverage:beer
13. House:tower == Cigar:prince
14. House:gothic-revival is on the left or right of Birthday:december
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
